item.title: By: Carole Olinger
item.dc:creator: Carole Olinger
item.description: I truly envy you for all the impressions you’re collecting. This is so inspiring - YOU are so inspiring! Thanks for keeping us updated, besides walking hours and hours a day! You rock!
